{"tid":494210,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋傳「隱身衣」片段　稱屬未來港大校長張翔發明　央視揭後期加工","createTime":"2017-12-09T11:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T17:19:52.000Z","uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"871dbb0f3abb7f18a9ab3b126873178fb8e73b43","tid":494210,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"香港大學校長馬斐森下月底離任，有傳專門研究隱形材料技術的美籍內地學者張翔，將會成為新校長。近日社交網站及Whatsapp上均流傳一段來歷不明的影片，宣稱是張翔的「隱身衣」發明，片中男子使用「隱身衣」後隨即消失。不過央視今日引述視頻製作公司專業人士，認為影片是使用了電腦後期加工。<br />\n<br />\n近日FB流傳影片，標題為「未來港大校長張翔發明的隱形衣？」影片可見一名男子在公園漫步，並取出了一塊透明布料放在身體前，其身驅隨即隱形，與背面的公園園景融為一體。<br />\n<br />\n該影片亦有在Whatsapp廣傳，短訊附有信息文字：「候選港大新校長點叻？看看下面視頻便知道」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CIBaTVwAVVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCIBaTVwAVVE&d=MbehmNRN3VdOyAzoHD%2FQARv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6286beed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CIBaTVwAVVE</a><br />\n<br />\n不過央視今日報道<a href=\"http://m.news.cctv.com/m/a/index.shtml?id=ARTI3wsuuYBjaBV8Uqi5C6HJ171207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.news.cctv.com%2Fm%2Fa%2Findex.shtml%3Fid%3DARTI3wsuuYBjaBV8Uqi5C6HJ171207&d=MbehmNRN3VdOyAzoHD%2FQARv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=6ba3254c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.news.cctv.com/m/a/index.shtml?id=ARTI3wsuuYBjaBV8Uqi5C6HJ171207</a>，點出影片可能有造假之嫌。報道引述視頻製作公司專業人士指，影片是通過後期摳像技術合成，有不少視頻後期合成軟件都可以做出這樣的效果。他解釋指只要先拍攝無人純背景，之後找人拿著綠布再拍一遍，就可以軟件把綠布部分摳除，把兩次視頻合成，造出隱形衣效果。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指視頻上隱形布上隱約有一些閃光點，其實就是摳像上的定位點，是用來追踪用的。另外視頻也有穿崩鏡頭，有網友表示，片中男子「腳踢動的葉子在晃，但是布裡的葉子不晃，露餡了」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這段影片有造假之嫌，但張翔的確是研究隱形材料技術的專家，其代表作納米隱身衣研究曾被美國《時代》雜誌列為2008年十大科學發現，認為其研究可能令「隱身衣」成真。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E9%9A%B1%E8%BA%AB%E8%A1%A3-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B1%AC%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%BC%B5%E7%BF%94%E7%99%BC%E6%98%8E-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%8F%AD%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E9%259A%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25BF%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&d=MbehmNRN3VdOyAzoHD%2FQARv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=23e49d30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E9%259A%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25A1%25A3-%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25BF%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2598%258E-%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25B7%25A5%2F&h=277c6b4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E9%9A%B1%E8%BA%AB%E8%A1%A3-%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E7%A8%B1%E5%B1%AC%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E5%BC%B5%E7%BF%94%E7%99%BC%E6%98%8E-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%8F%AD%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%9F%E5%8A%A0%E5%B7%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"953f7812d5f5591103d9b971bcd32f9bf0a53435","tid":494210,"uid":55511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:46:03.000Z","msg":"好簡單 佢係候選人 梗係要整啲新聞比自己<br />\n不過fail左咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe567897a2b3cfd8929edb542f04109a739bcae","tid":494210,"uid":33422,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"央視踢返爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  內戰"},{"pid":"e1a87da469c160b5993149c7504fad148102f849","tid":494210,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"1:02 手指都隱埋形 <img src=